sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 💻 Developer
    participant Script as 📜 deploy-demo.sh
    participant Podman as 🐳 Podman
    participant Systemd as ⚙️ systemd
    participant FreeIPA as 🔐 FreeIPA DNS
    participant Traefik as 🌐 Traefik

    Dev->>Script: ./scripts/deploy-demo-ubi.sh
    activate Script

    Script->>Podman: Create secret (demo-postgres-password)
    Podman-->>Script: ✅ Secret created

    Script->>Script: Copy quadlets to /etc/containers/systemd/
    Script->>Systemd: systemctl daemon-reload
    Systemd-->>Script: ✅ Quadlets loaded

    Script->>Podman: Create demo-net network
    Podman-->>Script: ✅ Network created

    Script->>Systemd: systemctl start demo-db-ubi.service
    activate Systemd
    Systemd->>Podman: Pull ghcr.io/jkirklan/demo-db-ubi:latest
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Image pulled
    Systemd->>Podman: Create container (demo-db-ubi)
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Container created

    Note over Podman: PostgreSQL initializes<br/>Creates schema<br/>(~15 seconds)

    Podman->>Podman: Health check (pg_isready)
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Healthy
    deactivate Systemd

    Script->>Systemd: systemctl start demo-webapp-ubi.service
    activate Systemd
    Systemd->>Podman: Pull ghcr.io/jkirklan/demo-webapp-ubi:latest
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Image pulled
    Systemd->>Podman: Create container (demo-webapp-ubi)
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Container created

    Note over Podman: Node.js starts<br/>Connects to database<br/>(~5 seconds)

    Podman->>Podman: Health check (curl /health)
    Podman-->>Systemd: ✅ Healthy
    deactivate Systemd

    Script-->>Dev: ✅ Demo deployed at localhost:3000

    Note over Dev,Traefik: Optional: Add DNS and Traefik routing

    Dev->>FreeIPA: ipa dnsrecord-add demo-ubi --a-rec=192.168.1.150
    FreeIPA-->>Dev: ✅ DNS record added

    Dev->>Traefik: Deploy demo-routes.yml
    Traefik->>FreeIPA: DNS lookup (demo-ubi.lab.kubelet.org)
    FreeIPA-->>Traefik: 192.168.1.150

    Traefik->>Podman: Proxy to localhost:3000
    Podman-->>Traefik: ✅ Response

    deactivate Script

    Dev->>Traefik: HTTPS://demo-ubi.lab.kubelet.org
    Traefik->>Podman: HTTP://192.168.1.151:3000
    Podman-->>Traefik: JSON response
    Traefik-->>Dev: HTTPS response
